krantiveera sangolli rayanna ( english : legendary warrior sangolli rayanna ) is a 2012 indian historical biographical film kannada film directed by naganna and produced by anand appugol . darshan , jayaprada and nikita thukral play lead roles . the film is about sangolli rayanna , a prominent freedom fighter from karnataka , who fought the british till he was captured and executed in 1831 . he was the army chief of the kingdom of kittur ruled at the time by kittur rani chennamma . kranti veera sangolli rayanna was produced at a cost of an estimated rs 30 crore and collected approximately â‚¹ 30 crore in 22 days of screening in karnataka .